"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890370","Department for International Trade","false","2018-05-02","<p>The Board of Trade met at the University of Central Lancashire in Preston on 29 March 2018.</p><p>The meeting was attended by the Advisers to the Board of Trade, as stated on <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/news/international-trade-secretary-dr-liam-fox-convenes-a-new-board-of-trade-to-ensure-the-benefits-of-free-trade-are-spread-throughout-the-uk" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/international-trade-secretary-dr-liam-fox-convenes-a-new-board-of-trade-to-ensure-the-benefits-of-free-trade-are-spread-throughout-the-uk</a>, my Rt Hon Friends the Secretary of State for International Trade, the Secretary of State for Wales, my Hon Friend the Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State for Northern Ireland and I. The Lord Mayor of London also attended as an Adviser.</p>","Chelsea and Fulham","Greg Hands","137625 ; 137626","2018-05-02T14:51:53.793Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890370/answer","Biography information for Greg Hands","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890370/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890370/answer",,,,,,,,,"202","International Trade","International Trade","2018-04-24","Board of Trade: Meetings","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Trade, when the most recent meeting was of the Board of Trade.","false","Biography information for Peter Kyle","Hove","Peter Kyle","137624"
